data.description: This lovely 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is located in the Newport Golf Club Community. Open floor plan with a large family room and fireplace. The bright, white kitchen overlooks the family room and features granite countertops, center island, a lot of cabinet space, breakfast area and bar, with a separate formal dining room perfect for entertaining. The primary suite offers 2 walk-in closets, dual vanities, walk-in shower, and garden tub. The home sits on a large lot with a covered patio overlooking the backyard.
